cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.AR, cs.SY, cs.MM

The paper discusses the challenges and opportunities in network densification, energy efficiency, interference management, and mobility management, which are all related to the field of network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also discusses coordinated multipoint (CoMP) and device-to-device (D2D) communications, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and augmented reality (cs.AR). The paper proposes a separation architecture as a solution, which involves system-level optimization (cs.SY) and multimedia (cs.MM) applications. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI, followed by cs.IT, cs.AR, cs.SY, and cs.MM.
